 "Create the case story. A good case is one \nthat describes a controversy or sets the scene by describing the characters \ninvolved and the situation. It should also allow for some action to be taken \nin order to gain resolution of the situation.": "Criar o objectivo da hist\u00f3ria. Um bom objectivo \u00e9 aquele \nque descreve a controv\u00e9rsia ou configura  a cena descrevendo os seus intervenientes \nenvolvidos na situa\u00e7\u00e3o. Deve permitir iniciar algumas ac\u00e7\u00f5es \nno sentido de obter a resolu\u00e7\u00e3o da situa\u00e7\u00e3o.  ", 
